replies.body:
Thank you for understanding STVNSTAR. You seem to understand why this may be an issue.

@Nynetynyne He is a Rioter that was in talks to become management for CW. The argument that he had no authority is naivety at least and blind ignorance in the extreme. 

You don't have to be in an official position to tamper with supposed power. I will agree that Deficio probably didn't intentionally cause an issue.
